properties.flavorText: Now you can fortify your gates on the go!
A section of defensive wall destroyed many years ago. Great care was taken in the creation of this defense; geometric carvings cover the bulwark.
The last jar of sap from an unusual cave tree planted by Monster.
A carefully carved length of cavernwood that, at first glance, looks like a dangerous snake.
Stitched into the armlet is the insignia for a fallen kingdom that used to live deep under the Great Cabran Mountain.
An elder shaman looking to expanding his influence outside the Cavernwood.
